268
00:13:37,417 --> 00:13:38,617
Saya nak balik ke Maktab Diraja.

269
00:13:40,258 --> 00:13:41,497
Saya dah lama berfikir.

270
00:13:42,857 --> 00:13:45,657
Sejak masuk ke Maktab Diraja,
