300
00:15:05,818 --> 00:15:06,578
Saya balik dulu.

301
00:15:07,778 --> 00:15:08,657
Cepat balik berehat.

302
00:15:18,977 --> 00:15:19,497
Cepatlah balik.

303
00:15:32,097 --> 00:15:32,617
Bai Shi,

304
00:15:32,643 --> 00:15:33,799
(Kediaman Komandan Agung)

305
00:15:33,857 --> 00:15:34,818
saya nak masuk ke istana esok.

306
00:15:36,138 --> 00:15:36,818
Tak meminang?

307
00:15:37,338 --> 00:15:38,458
Saya perlu minta baginda

308
00:15:38,458 --> 00:15:40,338
mengurniakan jawatan
kepada Sang Qi dulu.

309
00:15:40,417 --> 00:15:41,657
Jika saya meminang dulu,

310
00:15:42,338 --> 00:15:43,258
semua orang akan tahu bahawa

311
00:15:43,258 --> 00:15:44,338
Sang Qi ialah bakal isteri saya.

312
00:15:45,497 --> 00:15:46,778
Desas-desus manusia
pada masa itu amat menakutkan.

313
00:15:46,778 --> 00:15:49,258
Mereka akan kata bahawa Sang Qi
dapat singgah di Maktab Diraja

314
00:15:49,258 --> 00:15:50,297
oleh sebab kuasa pengaruh orang lain.

315
00:15:51,737 --> 00:15:52,898
Tak boleh biar dia
tanggung tekanan sebegini.

316
00:15:53,537 --> 00:15:54,778
Tuan memang berfikir dengan menyeluruh.

317
00:16:58,338 --> 00:16:59,297
Yan Yunzhi.

318
00:16:59,818 --> 00:17:00,698
Patik di sini.

319
00:17:00,698 --> 00:17:02,218
Awak masuk ke istana
secara khas hari ini.

320
00:17:02,218 --> 00:17:03,818
Adakah awak nak tunjukkan macam mana

321
