366
00:18:53,749 --> 00:18:54,620
(Dikurniakan jawatan
Pendokumen Maktab Diraja)

367
00:18:56,698 --> 00:18:57,618
Yan Yunzhi,

368
00:18:58,738 --> 00:18:59,738
macam mana jika beta merupakan

369
00:18:59,738 --> 00:19:01,057
orang yang membantah itu?

370
00:19:03,297 --> 00:19:06,818
Bukankah tuanku dah menulis
pelantikan Sang Qi

371
00:19:06,818 --> 00:19:07,738
sebentar tadi?

372
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:09,580
