00:21:15,017 --> 00:21:17,098
Rasa-rasanya, awak tak gembira.

421
00:21:21,177 --> 00:21:21,897
Maaf.

422
00:21:23,818 --> 00:21:25,818
Saya tidak mendapat

423
00:21:25,858 --> 00:21:26,978
jawatan Pendokumen untuk awak.

424
00:21:29,057 --> 00:21:30,137
Terkejut pula saya!

425
00:21:30,137 --> 00:21:31,897
Saya ingat perkara penting apa
yang sedang awak cakap.

426
00:21:31,897 --> 00:21:33,498
Hal ini sudah diselesaikan.

427
00:21:39,218 --> 00:21:40,377
Rupa-rupanya, awak dah tahu.

428
00:21:40,377 --> 00:21:41,297
Ya,

429
00:21:41,338 --> 00:21:42,578
terima kasih kepada Zhuo Wenyuan

430
00:21:42,578 --> 00:21:44,498
kerana sampaikan permintaan
melalui Jabatan Pegawai.

431
00:21:44,537 --> 00:21:46,498
Saya sudah merupakan
Pendokumen Maktab Diraja sekarang.

432
00:21:46,498 --> 00:21:48,218
Saya merupakan rakan sekerja awak.

433
00:21:49,738 --> 00:21:51,017
Zhuo Wenyuan?

434
00:21:51,017 --> 00:21:51,578
Ya.

435
00:21:51,578 --> 00:21:52,257
Dia dan awak...

436
00:21:53,338 --> 00:21:53,858
Tuan Yan,

437
00:21:55,137 --> 00:21:56,897
