dalam pertandingan wusyu ini.

728
00:37:42,538 --> 00:37:43,817
Saya takkan biar Yan Yunzhi

729
00:37:43,817 --> 00:37:44,778
merampas Sang Qi.

730
00:37:45,738 --> 00:37:47,657
